---
title: Frijoles Fresca Bowls with Tomato & Pepper Jack
description: Rice and beans are an iconic duo. The classic combo is simple, nourishing, and super easy to whip up. Well, our chefs have officially broken the pair out of their comfort-zone (in the very best way)! The results? Creamy black beans stewed with poblano and tangy salsa verde, then ladled over fluffy jasmine rice and topped with juicy diced tomato, pepper jack, and spiced crema. One bite and you’ll be wondering where these bowls have BEAN all your life.
